{"17735": {"html": "<style>.b2b-black, .b2b-black * { color:#000 !important; }</style>\n<div class=\"b2b-black\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<thead><tr style=\"background:#000;color:#fff;\"><th style=\"padding:6px;text-align:left;color:#fff !important;\">ŠUNS SVORIS</th><th style=\"padding:6px;text-align:center;color:#fff !important;\">REKOMENDUOJAMAS KONSERVO KIEKIS</th></tr></thead>\n<tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:6px;font-weight:bold;border:1px solid #ddd;\">5 kg</td><td style=\"padding:6px;text-align:center;border:1px solid #ddd;\">340 – 390 g</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:6px;font-weight:bold;border:1px solid #ddd;\">10 kg</td><td style=\"padding:6px;text-align:center;border:1px solid #ddd;\">565 – 655 g</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:6px;font-weight:bold;border:1px solid #ddd;\">15 kg</td><td style=\"padding:6px;text-align:center;border:1px solid #ddd;\">765 – 890 g</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:6px;font-weight:bold;border:1px solid #ddd;\">20 kg</td><td style=\"padding:6px;text-align:center;border:1px solid #ddd;\">950 – 1100 g</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:6px;font-weight:bold;border:1px solid #ddd;\">30 kg</td><td style=\"padding:6px;text-align:center;border:1px solid #ddd;\">1290 – 1495 g</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:6px;font-weight:bold;border:1px solid #ddd;\">40 kg</td><td style=\"padding:6px;text-align:center;border:1px solid #ddd;\">1600 – 1850 g</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"font-size:11px;margin-top:6px;\">Šaltinis: gamintojo (Animonda) GranCarno linijos rekomendacija. Konkretūs kiekiai gali nežymiai skirtis pagal skonį – atsižvelkite į gyvūno svorį, amžių ir aktyvumą.</p>\n</div>\n", "type": "SET_GRANCARNO"}, "19513": {"html": "<style>.b2b-black, .b2b-black * { color:#000 !important; }</style>\n<div class=\"b2b-black\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<thead><tr style=\"background:#000;color:#fff;\"><th style=\"padding:6px;text-align: